mar-Super-Bowl-2025-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kendrick-Lamar-Super-Bowl-2025-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kendrick-Lamar-Super-Bowl-2025-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>艺术总监雪莉·罗杰斯（Shelly Rodgers）说，肯德里克·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）</a>的超级碗半场表演的灵感来自视频游戏。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/ranking-the-10-best-super-bowl-halftime-shows-in-history-3394980">排名历史上10个最佳超级碗半场表演</a></li></ul><p>在周日晚上（2月9日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kendrick-lamar-full-2025-super-bowl-halftime-show-3836498">拉马尔成为第一个将活动的独奏说唱歌手</a>。在演出期间， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a> ，塞缪尔·杰克逊<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kendrick-lamar-hit-out-at-drake-during-super-bowl-halftime-show-2025-performance-i-want-to-play-their-favourite-song-but-you-know-they-like-to-sue-3836386">（</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/samuel-l-jackson">Samuel L.</a></p><p>在演出期间，游戏迷上了社交媒体，分享了他们的兴奋，拉马尔的舞台似乎向PlayStation致敬，舞台的四个角落由游戏机控制器上通常发现的一个按钮代表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3836527" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3836527" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-3836527 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kedrick-Lamar-2025-Super-Bowl.jpg" alt="肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）在舞台上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kedrick-Lamar-2025-Super-Bowl.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kedrick-Lamar-2025-Super-Bowl-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kedrick-Lamar-2025-Super-Bowl-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kedrick-Lamar-2025-Super-Bowl-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kedrick-Lamar-2025-Super-Bowl-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kedrick-Lamar-2025-Super-Bowl-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3836527" class="wp-caption-text">肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）于2025年2月9日在路易斯安那州新奥尔良举行的凯撒超级舞会（Caesars Superdome）在苹果音乐超级碗Lix半场表演中演出。图片来源：史密斯/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>在对<em><a href="https://www.wired.com/story/true-story-behind-kendrick-lamar-super-bowl-halftime-show/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《连线》的</a></em>新采访中，艺术总监雪莉·罗杰斯（Shelly Rodgers）证实，在演出期间将拉马尔（Lamar）的生活描绘成视频游戏的概念来自说唱歌手本人。她说：“我认为这是象征性的，他可以接触年轻人。” “很多人都表明了他的旅程，穿越了美国梦。”</p><p>创意总监迈克·卡森（Mike Carson）补充说，该场上的“基本形状”旨在为说唱歌手提供一个简洁，易于理解的平台来讲述这个故事。 “ Dave Free（导演）和肯德里克（Dave Free）和肯德里克（Kendrick）确实是为了保持清洁和最低限度，因此我们凭借单色混凝土外观，使视频游戏主题通过对话，照明，编舞和音乐使视频游戏主题变得活跃起来。”</p><p> Production for the 13-minute gig involved more than 50 carts of staging and equipment – each weighing between 680 and 1590 kg while the GNX car had to be gutted and will never drive again.</p><p> Following the performance, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamars-not-like-us-streams-jump-by-430-per-cent-after-super-bowl-performance-3836793">streams for Lamar&#39;s Drake diss track &#39;Not Like Us&#39; jumped up 430 per cent</a> and the rapper also announced <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-sza-announce-2025-uk-european-stadium-tour-buy-tickets-3836665">the European leg of his &#39;Grand National&#39; co-headline stadium tour with SZA</a> . The run of shows kicks off in Cologne on July 2 and will include a massive show at London&#39;s Tottenham Hotspur Stadium. The tour will end in Stockholm on August 9. Tickets go on sale this Friday (February 14) at 9am local time and can be bought <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fkendrick-lamar-tickets%2Fartist%2F1480454" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> .</p><p> In other news, to celebrate the 25th anniversary of <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-sims"><em>The Sims</em></a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kim-petras">Kim Petras</a> has <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/kim-petras-xxx-simlish-25th-anniversary-the-sims-3836933">recorded &#39;Slut Pop&#39; cut &#39;XXX&#39; in Simlish</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/kendrick-lamar-super-bowl-halftime-show-inspired-video-games-3836944">Kendrick Lamar&#39;s Super Bowl Halftime show was inspired by video games, says collaborator</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
