21. It will be available as a single on Friday (14) 。 </p><p><iframe style="width: 100%; max-width: 660px; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 10px;" src="https://embed.music.apple.com/us/album/gods-of-rock-n-roll-orchestral-feat-steve-stevens/1790845473?i=1790846060" height="175" frameborder="0" sandbox="allow-forms allow-popups allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-storage-access-by-user-activation allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation"></iframe></p><p> As highlighted by <em><a href="https://consequence.net/2025/02/ozzy-osbourne-gods-of-rock-n-roll-chart-before-release/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Consequence</a></em> , the original track wasn&#39;t the only time that the Prince Of Darkness teamed up with Morrisson, as the two also worked together alongside Steve Stevens on a song called &#39;Crack Cocaine&#39; – which featured on the original version of &#39;The Morrison Project&#39;. The forthcoming new version of the album will also include two new versions of that track.</p><p> The upcoming single from Osbourne comes just days after the metal pioneer announced details of <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbath-final-show-birmingham-july-2025-metalla-slayer-pantera-line-up-tickets-3835042">the final-ever Black Sabbath live show, which will take place in Birmingham on July 5</a> . The hometown event will include a number of star-studded opening acts and special guests, including <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Metallica">Metallica</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Slayer">Slayer</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Pantera">Pantera</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Lamb-Of-God">Lamb Of God</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mastodon">Mastodon</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Alice-In-Chains">Alice In Chains</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/halestorm">Halestorm</a> , recent <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">Grammy</a> -winners <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">Gojira</a> and more.</p><p> <a href="/artists/tom-morello">Tom Morello</a> – the soloist and former <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rage-against-the-machine">Rage Against The Machine</a> guitarist – will also be appearing at the gig, serving as music director. In a statement, the musician described <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">Ozzy Osbourne</a> and co&#39;s final show as set to be “the greatest heavy metal show ever”. </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFu3ZyBzEea/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,6